        "name": "abetusk",
        "username": "abetusk",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.oshwa.org/abetusk/{size}/42_1.png",
        "created_at": "2015-06-06T19:11:35.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>My vote is for self certification.  I think the <a href=\"http://www.oshwa.org/2015/06/02/building-an-open-source-hardware-certification-with-oshwa/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">\u2018Self-Certification\u2019 </a>describes it well.  Most notably, allowing for easy and widespread adoption.</p>",
