        "name": "Suniel Kumar",
        "username": "sunielkumar",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v2/letter/s/f08c70/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2015-06-13T05:40:13.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Individuals, groups &amp; community - who make their works &amp; creation open are the driving force for Open source hardware . Self Certification should be be the way for promoting open source. A certification process should be created &amp; made available for following, like the best practises.</p>",
