      {
        "id": 146,
        "name": "antoine",
        "username": "antoine",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v2/letter/a/7ab992/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2015-06-17T04:27:40.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Pre-approval process by OSHWA could be great, but only based on an automatic declarative process like is done with CCC choice of license, proposing a specific sentence or logo to place on/with the openness hardware, with the link with the OSHWA definition certification, and a \u201creport certification abuse\u201d link.</p>\n<p>I\u2019m afraid any non-declarative or non-automatic process will be impossible to run for OSHWA.</p>",
