        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v2/letter/m/9fc348/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2015-06-30T12:58:32.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Self-certification for all but top level.<br>\nPre-approval for top level. (A fee may apply.)<br>\nMy reasoning in this is that for most people is hard to know if all components are open source or open standard.</p>",
